<p>Today's podcast takes a look at an open source project called <a href="http://ajaxian.com/archives/gordon-flash-runtime-implemented-in-javascript">Gordon</a> from <a href="http://www.xing.com/profile/Tobias_Schneider14">Tobias Schneider</a> (<a href="http://twitter.com/tobeytailor">@tobeytailor</a>) that enables <a href="http://www.adobe.com/products/flashplayer/">Adobe Flash</a> to run in an <a href="http://dev.w3.org/html5/spec/Overview.html">HTML5</a> browser using <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JavaScript">JavaScript</a>.  Additional links mentioned in this podcast include:</p>

